<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="occur-to-sb">occur to sb</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>被想到，浮现在脑中</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>it occurs to sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It occurred to her to phone the police.
她想到了给警察打电话。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>it occurs to sb + (that) 从句:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It occurred to him that he had an important conference to attend the next morning.
他突然想到第二天早上要参加一个重要会议。</p><footer>2011 湖北</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Not once did it occur to Michael that he could one day become a top student in his class.
迈克尔从未想到过有一天他能成为班上的优等生。</p><footer>2013 湖南</footer></div></div>